Directly after the repurchase of the dubious claims, the government will intervene aggressively to ensure that the amount paid to leaders is not exaggerated.
In order for the image to be complete, it is necessary to add that the existing golden parachutes are not modified. The cap is only for new contracts, this to motivate participation in the plan.
This is the first time in U.S. history that legal caps will be in place on the appointments of directors general - commented House Financial Benefits Committee Chair Barney Frank Democrat.
In addition, the state acquires a right to acquire shares in the banks participating in the plan, thereby reducing the risk of taxpayers, since they can even be winning in the case as soon as the economy and with it the saved banks fall back on their feet.
